A woman dumped her husband&#39;s body into a pit and poured it with concrete near Belgorod
In the Belgorod region, a woman confessed to killing her own husband, whom she threw into a waste pit and poured concrete, according to the website of the regional department of the RF IC.
It is noted that the suspect has been married to the murdered since 1999.
In recent years, the husband began to abuse alcohol, and after another quarrel, the woman decided to kill.
“When the husband fell asleep, the suspect tied his hands and feet, put a plastic bag over his head and crushed him with a pillow.
When her husband stopped showing signs of life, she wrapped the body in a carpet, took it out into the yard and hid it in a cesspool.
The next day, she called a concrete mixer and filled the pit with concrete,&quot; the department said.
Later, the woman reported that her husband was missing.
The relatives of the deceased contacted the police, who opened the pit and removed the body.
The investigation intends to ask the court to arrest the suspect.
The criminal investigation is currently ongoing.
